N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 456.6 - Duplicate snowmobile safety certificate

State Regulations

In the event that a snowmobile safety certificate is
lost, the youthful operator may obtain a duplicate snowmobile safety
certificate by making application to the bureau upon payment of a fee of
$1. Notes
